- Loading the Target Page to Source page without refreshing the whole web page called as Single Page Application.

- Loading the Target Page to Source Page Called as Routing.

- In AngularJS We Can Achieve Routings in 2 ways.

    1.ngRoute

    2.ui.router

Steps to Design the Single Page Application by using ngRoute Module.

1.Download the ngRoute Module by using bower.

2.Add the ngRoute Dependency.

3.create the Templates

4.Create the Controllers

5.Done the Mappings.

6.Create the Source Template


